{"tid":1638211,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"南華葉頌朗央視受訪無悔加入警隊 被舊友篤灰曾參與佔中","createTime":"2019-10-08T08:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T05:54:03.000Z","uid":68738,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3177e174d7a171d83145bab4f67b8df391a75afd","tid":1638211,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/FnhlYZcHDeC8BhTC3ogvmMne7iY=/1556x871/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/6UTPACIH2QIBCZ4T2WCBTAW264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FFnhlYZcHDeC8BhTC3ogvmMne7iY%3D%2F1556x871%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F6UTPACIH2QIBCZ4T2WCBTAW264.jpg&h=de4a2254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前港青足球代表葉頌朗去年掛靴投身警隊任見習督察，他早前曾於社交平台侮辱示威者「是一群趁機攪事的垃圾」，已引來球迷不滿，日前他更高調接受中央電視台訪問，表示加入警隊如同往日代表香港一樣引以為傲，明言無懼社會困局。然而有葉頌朗舊友向本報爆料，指他2014年曾參與佔領運動，當年更曾於社交平台發文，表示「堅持團結才有機會出現一絲的希望，求天佑我的香港」，今日的我打倒昨日的我，為人不齒。<br />\n<br />\n現效力港甲業餘隊南華的葉頌朗去年五月結束職業球員生涯，同年六月投考見習督察，現為柴灣特遣隊主管，日前他再接受中央電視台訪問，指代表香港是一件很驕傲的事，而任警察就似踢球一樣講求團隊精神和紀律。葉頌朗高調受訪，惟有讀者向《蘋果》報料，揭發葉頌朗14年佔中時曾走上街頭抗爭，又於社交網站自拍發文分享於金鐘通宵佔領後的感想，其時他撰文指「十幾萬人一齊高叫口號，高唱海闊天空，互相幫助......徹夜留守，並不好玩，個個都提心吊膽會半夜比人武力清場，又悶又辛苦，堅持團結才有機會出現一絲的希望，求天佑我的香港。」事過人變，五年過去，當日上街抗爭的葉頌朗已站在「武力清場」一方，「逆權運動」爆發後，更曾於社交平台侮辱示威者「是一群趁機攪事的垃圾」、「唔配做香港人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/Z44jocV5DegtPiY14LuS-hgCnT8=/732x1309/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/K6PEVGUQTJZZDM5QJNXOJOQPRA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FZ44jocV5DegtPiY14LuS-hgCnT8%3D%2F732x1309%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FK6PEVGUQTJZZDM5QJNXOJOQPRA.jpg&h=4aa40005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/kthughV58atEW1ehcRwmbrEddCM=/1006x1600/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/DGGD3KEKJXLH6COZJCIPJCWVX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FkthughV58atEW1ehcRwmbrEddCM%3D%2F1006x1600%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FDGGD3KEKJXLH6COZJCIPJCWVX4.jpg&h=85f717b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edfcc66534157ef21a9e5f4a5fc524501fec4323","tid":1638211,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:45:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">合法公民抗爭！！！！！你都唔想郁？？？？？？ 唔使旨意想贏！！！！！<br />\n快啲跟住做啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637669</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"ab6915d1b21bfa64e4f59221b344fee17c9ca258","tid":1638211,"uid":174498,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做運動員失敗 結果轉工做一份更失敗嘅職業"},{"pid":"b2f193a12eebcf53d28b4aef8525c2be9418f96e","tid":1638211,"uid":153781,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:46:07.000Z","msg":"一定係d打卡撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f640895d9fafc9f4d75ab9fee1dfafe7f4ee4af","tid":1638211,"uid":67903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:49:10.000Z","msg":"仲有班人話要加入警隊改革"},{"pid":"36f7d1baac6b8bc67066d3cbb6a7d217bda8ab44","tid":1638211,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:50:39.000Z","msg":"有無港甲撚幫手係球場上熱血飛剷？<br />\n一腳印落上5寸下5寸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2d9ccb18b80fd930a81979ae2ac954940cb2fa","tid":1638211,"uid":76958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:50:45.000Z","msg":"波牛都考到pi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c